channel.title: [PI] Random Event?
channel.description: Anyone have a real close 100 percent random event for the petes jail so it randomly teleports you about 1 hour - 6 hours of being on the game and teleports you to the coordinates for the place. Make it so if you don't get out of the event in about 30 min it logs you in the source as an auto clicker or a botter and teleports u to ur old coordinates?
